cdata.name: XinFin Coin
cdata.desc:
XDCE Protocolis an initiative of XinFin.org to built a Hybrid Blockchain architecture. The protocol purposes to eliminate the inefficiencies in global trade, financing and to enable financial institutions to provide real-time settlement as well as enabling cross-border smart contracts.

XinFinCoin (XDCE) will be used to access the project services.
